    "description": "🗺️ **Atlas: FM Global’s Next-Generation Geospatial Intelligence Platform**\n\n**Atlas** is FM Global’s enterprise-grade mapping solution designed to analyze and act on **natural hazard risks** with enhanced functionality, deeper insights, and a vastly improved user experience. It replaces the legacy **RiskView** platform and integrates seamlessly into systems like **CEVO Business Technology Platform (BTP)**, **Polaris**, **Map Center**, and the **Climate Resilience Tracker**.",
